=====================================
Element-wise Matrix/Vector Operations                                   [TOC]
=====================================

For-Loops provides the easiest, most readable and most efficient way to do
element-wise operations.  However, in the case of matrices this requires
you to order loops depending on row and column major storage.  In FLENS you
can use special _index variables_ to iterate over a general or triangular
matrix the best order.

